{"descriptions":[{"id":437,"title":"Ritual for Guiding/Helping the Dead (e.g. into a Pure Land)","content":"\u003ch1\u003eRelated Terms\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egshin po\u0026rsquo;am tshe \u0026lsquo;das rjes su \u0026lsquo;dzin pa\u0026rsquo;i cho ga;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egshin sbyang;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esbyang chog;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egshin po rnams kyi rnam shes gnas spor byed pa'i cho ga;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egshin chog;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egshin chos;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egnas chog,\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egnas \u0026lsquo;dren,\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egnas dgongs,\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egnas lung\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eExample Texts\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMi \u0026lsquo;khrugs pa\u0026rsquo;i sgo nas gshin po rjes gzung gi cho ga\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W16185\"\u003eLho sgo\u0026rsquo;i cho ga\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eSecondary Sources\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003c!--[if gte mso 9]\u003e\u003cxml\u003e Normal   0         false   false   false                             MicrosoftInternetExplorer4 \u003c/xml\u003e\u003c![endif]--\u003e\u003c!--[if gte mso 9]\u003e\u003cxml\u003e \u003c/xml\u003e\u003c![endif]--\u003e\u003c!--[if !mso]\u003e \u003cspan class=\"mceItemObject\"   classid=\"clsid:38481807-CA0E-42D2-BF39-B33AF135CC4D\" id=ieooui\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003cmce:style\u003e\u003c!  st1\\:*{behavior:url(#ieooui) } --\u003e \u003c!--[endif]--\u003e\u003c!--  --\u003e\u003c!--[if gte mso 10]\u003e \u003cmce:style\u003e\u003c!   /* Style Definitions */  table.MsoNormalTable \t{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\"; \tmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0; \tmso-tstyle-colband-size:0; \tmso-style-noshow:yes; \tmso-style-parent:\"\"; \tmso-padding